               <p>I am a constable. I pursued the prisoner, and took him into custody; he said a boy gave him the copper, but he did not know him.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>He looks like a bigger thief than myself;<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177712150013"></xptr> I know nothing of it. That man robbed Coleman-street church.</p>
